body.description: The large 25-person metal SmartCompliance First Aid Food Service Cabinet is perfect for individual restaurants or restaurant chains. The unique cabinet design eliminates disorganized and missing supplies, while the clearly labeled compartments create a cabinet that is easy to use and restock. The expansion pocket allows you to customize your cabinet to meet your specific needs. The SmartCompliance cabinet SmartTab ezRefill System is a simple but effective way for reordering and restocking, revolutionizing the replenishment process. It is quick, easy, and cost effective. As supplies are used, Smart Tab ezRefill reminder tabs notify you when it is time to reorder supplies and puts reorder information at your fingertips. The FAO SafetyHub, a mobile requisition app, also allows you to monitor cabinet usage to stay compliant and know when to reorder your refills. The metal case comes with a carrying handle. This large first aid kit can be mounted on a wall or other flat vertical surfaces.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 3, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Be Prepared Buy It
reviews.reviewText: I love it with 1 downside. The bandaid in it are junk. They don't stick well and should be replaced with some higher quality ones. I kept the cardboard display box and changed mine out with good ones. The rest of the kit seems well made. I added some Narcan to mine and it's screwed into the wall in my laundry room so anyone can get to it.. get yourself a LifeVac and you'll be set. A little security goes along way and this one is a win. Looks nice on the wall in my home too.
